<html lang="en">

  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style>
      body { background-color: #101010; color: #fff; font-family: Arial,
      sans-serif; padding: 20px; margin: 0; } .container { max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto; background-color: #1a1a1a; border-radius: 8px; overflow:
      hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); } .header {
      background-color: #1a1a1a; color: #2B7FFF; padding: 20px; text-align:
      center; border-top-left-radius: 8px; border-top-right-radius: 8px; }
      .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 24px; color: #fff; } .content {
      padding: 20px; background-color: #262626; } .content p { margin: 0 0 16px;
      line-height: 1.6; color: #e0e0e0; } .welcome-section { background-color:
      #1a1a1a; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; border-left:
      4px solid #2B7FFF; } .steps-section { background-color: #1a1a1a; padding:
      20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; } .step { margin-bottom: 20px;
      padding-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #333; } .step:last-child {
      border-bottom: none; margin-bottom: 0; } .step-number { color: #2B7FFF;
      font-weight: bold; margin-right: 10px; font-size: 18px; } .step-title {
      font-weight: bold; color: #2B7FFF; font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
      .step-description { color: #e0e0e0; margin-left: 24px; } .cta-button {
      display: inline-block; background-color: #2B7FFF; color: #1a1a1a
      !important; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: bold; margin: 10px 0; text-align: center; } .cta-button:hover
      { background-color: #5BA3FF; } a[href] { color: #1a1a1a !important; }
      .help-section { background-color: #1a1a1a; padding: 20px; border-radius:
      8px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #2B7FFF; } .footer {
      text-align: center; padding: 20px; font-size: 14px; color: #aaa;
      background-color: #1a1a1a; border-bottom-left-radius: 8px;
      border-bottom-right-radius: 8px; } .footer p { margin: 0; } .footer a {
      color: #2B7FFF; text-decoration: none; } .closing { text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0; padding: 20px; background-color: #1a1a1a; border-radius:
      8px; } .team-signature { font-weight: bold; color: #2B7FFF; margin-top:
      10px; } .tagline { font-style: italic; color: #aaa; margin-top: 5px; }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to Church Planting Institute</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <div class="welcome-section">
          <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
          <p>Thank you for joining Church Planting Institute!</p>
          <p>We're honored to partner with you as you deepen your calling and
            equip yourself for shepherding God's people.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="steps-section">
          <p
            style="font-weight: bold; color: #2B7FFF; font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 20px;"
          >What happens next?</p>

          <div class="step">
            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center;">
              <span class="step-number">1.</span>
              <span class="step-title">Complete Your Enrollment</span>
            </div>
            <div class="step-description">
              Our flagship course contains the full curriculum (video lectures,
              guided reflections, and ministry resources)
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="step">
            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center;">
              <span class="step-number">2.</span>
              <span class="step-title">Secure Your Seat (No Extra Fees)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="step-description">
              To make sure every dollar you invest goes directly into developing
              future training (not app-store fees) we process tuition on our own
              website.
            </div>
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 15px 0;">
              <a href="{{checkoutUrl}}" class="cta-button">Activate My Course
                Now</a>
            </div>
            <div class="step-description">
              Click the link above to finish enrollment and unlock the course
              immediately.
            </div>
            <div
              style="margin-top: 15px; padding: 10px; background-color: #333; border-radius: 6px; border-left: 4px solid #2B7FFF;"
            >
              <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #aaa;">
                <strong>⏰ Important:</strong>
                This link will expire on
                <span id="localExpirationDate">{{expirationDate}}</span>
                at
                <span id="localExpirationTime">{{expirationTime}}</span>
                {{#if isUTC}}(UTC timezone){{else}}({{timeZone}}
                  timezone){{/if}}. Please complete your enrollment before then.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="step">
            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center;">
              <span class="step-number">3.</span>
              <span class="step-title">Start Learning</span>
            </div>
            <div class="step-description">
              Once payment is confirmed, log back into the app and your course
              will appear in "My Library." You can study at your own
              pace—anytime, anywhere.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="closing">
          <p>Welcome to the community!</p>
          <p>Grace and peace,</p>
          <p class="team-signature">The Church Planting Institute Team</p>
          <p class="tagline">Empowering shepherds for global impact</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>If you have any issues, please contact
          <a target="_blank" href="mailto:bluehancedigital@gmail.com">our
            support team.</a>
        </p>
        <p>&copy; {{year}} Church Planting Institute. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>

</html>